<HEADLINE> Samba Renominated as WHO Regional Director for </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, September 9 (Xinhua) -- World Health Organization (WHO)
regional director for Africa Ebrahim Samba thanked African leaders
on Thursday for nominating him for a second term.
</P>
<P>
"I thank all African leaders most sincerely for giving me this
second opportunity to serve our people," Samba told the delegates
attending a WHO workshop in Harare.
</P>
<P>
