<HEADLINE> China's First Legislative Hearing Held in Guangzhou (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The members attending the hearing were selected from 30
candidates, and their professions include lawyer, professor and
entrepreneur. Among the 40 observers at the hearing were two
diplomatic officials from the United States and Australian
consulates in Guangzhou.
</P>
