map of troop redeployments in the West Bank to Palestinian leader
Yasser Arafat and explain to him from which area Israel will pull
out its troops, Israel Radio said.
</P>
<P>
Israeli and Palestinian officials met behind the closed doors
Thursday and discussed in details about the troop redeployment map
prepared by Israel in order to carry out the newly signed Sharm
El-Sheikh agreement, the Radio quoted government and military
officials as saying. (BC-Israel-Map)



