<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Manchester United boss Alex
Ferguson has been named Carling Manager of the Month for August
ahead of the game at Liverpool.
</P>
<P>
Alex has now won the award 10 times since joining Manchester
United as manager in 1986 -- more than any other club boss.
</P>
