<HEADLINE> Highlights of Today's Diplomatic News </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Following are the highlights
of the diplomatic news released by Xinhua here today.
</P>
<P>
NPC Vice-Chairman Meets Hungarian Guests
</P>
<P>
Buhe, vice-chairman of China's National People's Congress (NPC)
Standing Committee, met here today with Hamori Jozsef, minister
