<HEADLINE> TV Oratorical Competition to Be Held in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 10 (Xinhua) -- A television oratorical
competition with the theme "Celebrating Macao's Return to the
Motherland" is scheduled for October in Beijing.
</P>
<P>
The contest, co-sponsored by the Beijing TV Station, the Macao
Association of Chinese Culture and Arts, and several other
organizations, will celebrate Macao's return, popularize standard
Chinese and promote patriotism.
</P>
<P>
Residents of Beijing, Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan are eligible
to participate in the contest.
</P>
<P>
A group of scholars and experts from Beijing, Macao and Taiwan
will be invited to act as the judges.  
</P>
</TEXT>
