<HEADLINE> Chinese, Philippine FMs Meet </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AUCKLAND, New Zealand, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Foreign
Minister Tang Jiaxuan met here Friday with his Philippine
counterpart Domingo Siazon and they discussed bilateral relations
and regional issues of common concern.
</P>
<P>
Tang told Siazon that China attaches great importance to
developing friendly and cooperative relations with the Philippines
and that bilateral ties have by and large developed smoothly
thanks to the frequent exchange of visits between leaders of the
two countries.
</P>
<P>
