important for the two countries to build closer relations and
expand friendly cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Echoing Tang's comments, Siazon expressed the hope that the
Philippine-Chinese relations would be further strengthened through
contacts and exchange of visits between leaders of the two
countries.
</P>
<P>
Tang and Siazon met on the sidelines of the two-day 11th
Ministerial Meeting of the Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation
forum, which opened here Thursday. 
